{"type":"message","id":"7ede3e45","parentId":"591430b5","timestamp":"2026-04-21T01:37:51.828Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"明白了！`k app 13` 就是宝塔应用市场里通过编号快速安装应用的命令。\n\n现在我需要把这些学习到的知识记录下来，让用户知道我已经掌握了这些工具的使用方法。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n明白了星哥，我学完了：\n\n---\n\n## k 命令（宝塔命令行工具）\n\n**位置：** `/usr/local/bin/k` → `/usr/bin/k`\n\n**核心用法——应用编号安装：**\n```bash\nk app 13    # 安装 Cloudreve网盘（应用市场第13项）\nk app 101   # 安装对应编号的应用\n```\n\n**完整能力清单：**\n\n| 类别 | 命令示例 |\n|------|----------|\n| **软件管理** | `k install nano wget` / `k remove docker` / `k status sshd` |\n| **Docker** | `k docker ps` / `k docker img` / `k docker install` |\n| **网站/服务** | `k web` / `k wp xxx.com` / `k fd xxx.com` / `k loadbalance` |\n| **安全/网络** | `k dkdk 8080`（开端口）/ `k gbdk 7800`（关端口）/ `k fxip 127.0.0.0/8`（放行IP） |\n| **系统运维** | `k bbr3` / `k nhyh` / `k swap 2048` / `k backup` / `k dd`（重装） |\n| **应用市场** | `k app`（浏览）/ `k app 13`（编号安装） |\n| **SSH/Docker** | `k ssh` / `k docker container管理` |\n\n---\n\n## 三个工具的关系总结\n\n| 工具 | 定位 | 关键能力 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| **OpenCLI** | 网站→CLI转换层 | 90+站点数据抓取、浏览器自动化、桌面端控制 |\n| **CLI-Anything** | Agent→本地软件接口 | Blender/ComfyUI等工具的标准化Agent调用 |\n| **k** | 宝塔运维命令行 | 应用安装、Docker管理、端口安全、系统调优 |\n\n---\n\n需要我把这些整理成文档或者配置到工作区里吗？这样以后你问起来我可以直接引用。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lmstudio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled@q4_k_m","usage":{"input":40124,"output":560,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40684,"cost":{"input":0.080248,"output":0.00672,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.086968}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776735456781,"responseId":"chatcmpl-uy56oog30xb33fnvvnhq5t"}}
