{"type":"message","id":"381b121c","parentId":"14e55141","timestamp":"2026-04-21T03:10:08.200Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The pattern matching keeps failing because the Chinese character detection in Python regex isn't working as expected, or the line structure is different than I'm assuming. Let me take a completely different approach - I'll just read the raw output from grep and process it manually without relying on complex regex patterns for Chinese characters.\n\nLooking back at my earlier successful grep command:\n```\nsed -n '15480,16500p' /usr/local/bin/k | grep -E \"[0-9]+\\..*[面板|应用|网盘|工具|管理]\"\n\n\n```\n\nThis actually worked and gave me good results! The issue is just converting that output into a clean format. Let me capture the grep output directly and then process it with basic string splitting instead of trying to match Chinese characters in regex patterns.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"903942364","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 直接用 shell 处理，更可靠\ngrep_output=$(sed -n '15480,16500p' /usr/local/bin/k | grep -E \"[0-9]+\\..*[面板|应用|网盘|工具]\")\n\necho \"共找到 $(echo \"$grep_output\" | wc -l) 行应用数据\"\necho \"\"\necho \"提取结果:\"\necho \"==========================================\"\n\n# Parse line by line\nwhile IFS= read -r line; do\n    # Extract all numbered items using sed\n    echo \"$line\" | grep -oP '\\d+\\.\\s*\\S*\\s*[\\x{4e00}-\\x{9fff}][^\\$\\{\"]+' | \\\n        sed 's/\\./ /' | while read num rest; do\n            if [ ${#rest} -gt 2 ]; then\n                echo \"  $num: $(echo \"$rest\" | cut -d' ' -f1-6)\"\n            fi\n        done\ndone <<< \"$grep_output\"\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lmstudio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled@q4_k_m","usage":{"input":60057,"output":590,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60647,"cost":{"input":0.120114,"output":0.00708,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.127194}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776740994618,"responseId":"chatcmpl-g9afzb13sweeaaeoec9gss"}}
