{"type":"message","id":"5d5e3804","parentId":"f2ce657b","timestamp":"2026-04-21T11:32:54.046Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"dbhub 不是一个常见的数据库客户端工具，可能是指其他东西。让我检查一下是否有类似的 CLI 工具。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**`dbhub` 不是标准的数据库客户端工具。**\n\n根据搜索结果：\n- `dbhub` 可能指向 DBHub.io（一个 SQLite 云服务），但它不是本地数据库客户端\n- GitHub 上没有广泛使用的名为 `dbhub` 的数据库管理工具\n- 常见的数据库客户端是：\n  - **MySQL**: `mysql`, `mycli`, `dbeaver`\n  - **PostgreSQL**: `psql`, `pgcli`, `dbeaver`  \n  - **SQLite**: `sqlite3`\n  - **Redis**: `redis-cli`\n\n**当前环境情况：**\n| 数据库 | 客户端状态 |\n|--------|-----------|\n| MySQL | ❌ `mysql` 未安装 |\n| PostgreSQL | ❌ `psql` 未安装 |\n| Redis | ❌ `redis-cli` 未安装 |\n| SQLite | ⚠️ 需要检查 |\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"245349256","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which sqlite3 2>/dev/null || echo \"sqlite3 not installed\"; apt list --installed 2>/dev/null | grep -iE \"mysql|postgres|redis|sqlite\" | head -10"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lmstudio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-claude-4.6-opus-reasoning-distilled@q4_k_m","usage":{"input":68524,"output":312,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68836,"cost":{"input":0.137048,"output":0.003744,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.140792}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776771163331,"responseId":"chatcmpl-xdrkasfkd8siw0risuw28j"}}
